<note id="fs-idm397272000" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm391529904"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 3.8 The Constitutional Convention and Debates over Ratification</para>
<para id="fs-idm394632832"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: PCE Politics and Power</para>
<para id="fs-idm374721008"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 3I Explain the differing ideological positions on the structure and function of the federal government</para>
<para id="fs-idm402141072"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 3.2.II.E</para>
<para id="fs-idm396094432"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-1 Developments and Processes, HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Claims and Evidence in Sources, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
